      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i was looking at my mortgage statement from wells fargo and im kinda confused. i have a 30 year fixed at 6.5% and my monthly payment is like 2100. can u show me how much of that is actually going to principal vs interest in the 5th year vs the 25th year? i feel like i'm barely making a dent in the actual loan amount in the beginning.",
